section
  h3(id='req.cookies') req.cookies

  p.
    When the <code>cookieParser()</code> middleware is used, this object
    defaults to <code>{}</code>. Otherwise, it contains the cookies sent by
    the user-agent.

  +js.
    // Cookie: name=tj
    req.cookies.name
    // => "tj"

  p.
    Please refer to <a href="https://github.com/expressjs/cookie-parser">cookie-parser</a> for additional documentation or any issues and concerns.